Package: compPLS
Type: Package
Title: Conduct Partial Least Squares regression for compositional data
Version: 1.1
Date: 2021-04-18
Author: Zachary Kurtz
Maintainer: Zachary Kurtz <zdkurtz@gmail.com>
Description: Partial Least Squares method on log-ratio transformed data.
    Methods for PLS, sparse PLS discriminant analysis and biplot plotting for
    high-dimensional compositions. Particularly microbial
    communities/microbiota OTU tables, as generated by 16S amplicon sequencing.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends:
   R (>= 4.0.0),
Imports:
    caret,
    ggplot2,
    MASS,
    pls,
    klaR,
    boot,
    grid,
    scales,
    kernlab
Suggests:
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Encoding: UTF-8
